and near-misses.

767
00:37:15,842 --> 00:37:17,713
I covered my eyes for that.

768
00:37:17,757 --> 00:37:19,672
What I liked was
the part at the end

769
00:37:19,715 --> 00:37:21,239
when they bounced
into the net

770
00:37:21,282 --> 00:37:23,806
and jumped up with that
big Wallenda smile.

771
00:37:23,849 --> 00:37:27,722
