785
00:38:05,369 --> 00:38:06,501
Yeah.

786
00:38:09,677 --> 00:38:10,853
Does it hurt?

787
00:38:12,768 --> 00:38:14,161
Your... Your finger?
The cut you...

788
00:38:14,204 --> 00:38:16,380
Oh, no.

789
00:38:16,423 --> 00:38:17,860
Oh, good, good. I'm glad.

790
00:38:21,081 --> 00:38:22,300
Thank you.

791
00:38:30,786 --> 00:38:32,657
[SIGHS HEAVILY]

792
00:38:32,701 --> 00:38:34,094
