802
00:39:14,481 --> 00:39:16,135
[EXCLAIMS]

803
00:39:16,179 --> 00:39:17,528
[CHILDREN LAUGHING]

804
00:39:20,445 --> 00:39:24,492
Daddy, Daddy.
It's still not breaking.

805
00:39:24,536 --> 00:39:28,061
Sweetie, the pinata's
going to crack open.
You'll get your candy.

806
00:39:30,932 --> 00:39:32,630
Has Daddy ever
let you down before?

807
00:39:33,021 --> 00:39:34,153
No.

808
00:39:34,197 --> 00:39:35,460
No.

809
00:39:36,373 --> 00:39:37,766
Sorry.

810
00:39:45,599 --> 00:39:47,907
I'll bring it right back.

811
00:39:48,820 --> 00:39:50,083
[SIGHS]

812
00:39:50,126 --> 00:39:51,431
Knock it out.

813
00:39:59,527 --> 00:40:01,876
[CHILDREN YELLING]

814
00:40:14,063 --> 00:40:15,150
[GAGGING]

815
00:40:24,726 --> 00:40:26,248
Am I dead?

816
00:40:26,293 --> 00:40:28,121
Yeah. Yeah, you're dead.

817
00:40:29,818 --> 00:40:31,036
Who are you?

818
00:40:31,079 --> 00:40:32,429
Me? Mason.

819
00:40:36,476 --> 00:40:37,695
You're not the clown?

820
00:40:37,739 --> 00:40:38,784
[CHUCKLING]
No, I'm not the fucking clown.

821
00:40:39,653 --> 00:40:41,568
What were you doing here?

822
00:40:41,612 --> 00:40:45,530
Well, I was...
I took your soul
before you, you know...

823
00:40:45,572 --> 00:40:47,269
And now I'm
supposed to escort you
to your lights.

824
00:40:47,313 --> 00:40:50,490
No, what were you doing?

825
00:40:50,534 --> 00:40:53,494
You made obscene
balloon animals
for my daughter.

826
00:40:53,538 --> 00:40:56,018
You insulted all my guests,

827
00:40:56,061 --> 00:40:57,932
and the whole time
you knew I was gonna die?

828
00:40:58,934 --> 00:41:00,369
Is this a joke?

829
00:41:06,724 --> 00:41:09,554
This is how she'll
remember her birthday?

830
00:41:09,597 --> 00:41:11,512
Do you want to come with me?
I'm gonna take you
to your lights...

831
00:41:11,556 --> 00:41:12,860
Stay away from me.

832
00:41:13,601 --> 00:41:15,036
Stay away from my family.

833
00:41:15,864 --> 00:41:17,431
Just... Just go.

834
00:41:46,677 --> 00:41:49,724
[GEORGE]:  Life always seemed
to be about two things,

835
00:41:49,768 --> 00:41:52,684
feeling bad
and then feeling better.

836
00:41:52,726 --> 00:41:55,251
For me,
the feeling bad
part came pretty easy.

837
00:41:57,601 --> 00:42:00,213
But the feeling better part,
how to make
myself feel better,

838
00:42:02,302 --> 00:42:04,217
I never got that part down.

839
00:42:08,090 --> 00:42:09,788
[LEAD SNAPS][GROANS]

840
00:42:09,831 --> 00:42:11,746
These No. 2 soft always break.

841
00:42:11,789 --> 00:42:14,619
I keep telling you
to buy the No. 4s,
but you don't listen.

842
00:42:16,969 --> 00:42:18,536
What's with the sad face?

843
00:42:18,579 --> 00:42:22,757
Some sad story.
Rent's due,
job sucks, cat's pregnant.

844
00:42:22,800 --> 00:42:24,454
You haven't seen
Mason lately, have you?

845
00:42:26,717 --> 00:42:28,023
Kiffany, can I get
some coffee, please?

846
00:42:28,849 --> 00:42:31,112
Why do you drink
coffee so late?

847
00:42:31,157 --> 00:42:32,898
You don't sleep as it is.

848
00:42:32,940 --> 00:42:35,204
Make that an espresso.
Thank you.

849
00:42:36,248 --> 00:42:38,293
Little Miss Cranky Pants.

850
00:42:38,338 --> 00:42:40,166
Whatever oats
you're sowing at this moment,

851
00:42:43,429 --> 00:42:45,737
whatever need you feel
to make some
kind of a statement

