853
00:42:51,829 --> 00:42:53,266
Is it something I did?

854
00:42:53,309 --> 00:42:54,833
Nothing's wrong.

855
00:42:56,835 --> 00:42:58,793
I got a promotion.

856
00:42:58,836 --> 00:43:00,141
What kind of
promotion did you get?

857
00:43:00,186 --> 00:43:03,449
Two more big bills
a week. Hunge.Huh.

858
00:43:03,492 --> 00:43:05,016
I joined the Police Academy.

859
00:43:05,059 --> 00:43:06,409
No, you didn't.

860
00:43:06,452 --> 00:43:07,976
[RUBE]: Yes, she did.

861
00:43:08,019 --> 00:43:09,847
They want more days,
these Happy Time people?

862
00:43:12,240 --> 00:43:13,938
I think you should
decline the offer.

863
00:43:13,981 --> 00:43:16,157
Fuck that.
It's done. I'm doing it.

864
00:43:16,202 --> 00:43:17,376
Roxy,
give us a moment, will you?

865
00:43:20,771 --> 00:43:23,295
Why can't I do this?
I'm doing this.

866
00:43:23,338 --> 00:43:25,297
She's joining
the fucking Police Academy.

867
00:43:25,340 --> 00:43:27,865
Roxy is not your concern.

868
00:43:27,909 --> 00:43:29,563
I'm just worried
that you're
taking on too much.

869
00:43:32,304 --> 00:43:35,177
People love to take roses
and they forget
about the thorns.

870
00:43:35,221 --> 00:43:37,048
