now, that's really beautiful,

871
00:43:37,092 --> 00:43:39,311
but I'm taking the promotion.

872
00:43:45,360 --> 00:43:47,188
Uh-uh. I wouldn't do that.

873
00:43:48,713 --> 00:43:49,887
What did she do now?

874
00:43:49,931 --> 00:43:51,541
Nice cross.

875
00:43:51,585 --> 00:43:53,108
Have any trouble
getting the blood off?

876
00:43:53,152 --> 00:43:54,806
[DAISY]: No,
just soap and water.

877
00:43:54,849 --> 00:43:56,590
[RUBE]: I just think
you should go in there
tomorrow morning

878
00:43:56,634 --> 00:44:01,159
