I want more money.

880
00:44:04,858 --> 00:44:07,034
"I want, I want."

881
00:44:08,688 --> 00:44:09,820
Look, Peanut...

882
00:44:09,864 --> 00:44:11,605
Don't call me that.

883
00:44:17,742 --> 00:44:22,746
I just think all that wanting
is not so good at this point,

884
00:44:22,789 --> 00:44:25,574
