about your promotion.

885
00:44:25,619 --> 00:44:28,882
Well, as much
as I've enjoyed
this little pow-wow,

886
00:44:28,927 --> 00:44:30,755
I think I'm just going to do
what I'm going to do.

887
00:44:34,409 --> 00:44:36,282
[KIFFANY]: Miss,
your espresso?

888
00:44:36,324 --> 00:44:37,762
I don't want it.

889
00:44:37,804 --> 00:44:39,197
We made it.
Somebody's got to pay for it.

890
00:44:40,807 --> 00:44:43,463
She's a cop.
