everything for free?

891
00:44:44,943 --> 00:44:47,119
[KIFFANY]: I thought
you were a meter maid.

892
00:44:47,161 --> 00:44:49,164
[ROXY]: Well, I'm a cop now.

893
00:44:49,208 --> 00:44:51,905
Good for you, baby.
Coffee's free for cops.

894
00:44:52,777 --> 00:44:54,735
Un-fucking-real.

895
00:44:59,739 --> 00:45:01,481
