you're a cop?

896
00:45:01,523 --> 00:45:03,309
I joined the Police
Academy this afternoon.

897
00:45:05,353 --> 00:45:06,746
Yeah, I don't
think I care for that.

898
00:45:43,827 --> 00:45:45,264
[THUNDER RUMBLING]

