919
00:47:48,648 --> 00:47:50,215
Go to bed, Daisy.

920
00:47:52,826 --> 00:47:55,697
So, Rube doesn't
want you at Happy Time.
That makes you unhappy.

921
00:47:55,742 --> 00:47:57,483
Delores wants
you at Happy Time

922
00:47:57,525 --> 00:47:58,918
but just so long
as you're unhappy.

923
00:47:58,963 --> 00:48:00,311
It just sounds like a plan.

924
00:48:02,009 --> 00:48:04,184
Life sucks, and then you die,

925
00:48:04,228 --> 00:48:06,318
and then it still sucks.

926
00:48:08,972 --> 00:48:10,103
What's with the cross?

927
00:48:11,889 --> 00:48:13,106
I don't know. I like it.

928
00:48:13,150 --> 00:48:14,326
What are you,
like, Catholic now?

929
00:48:14,369 --> 00:48:16,197
[CLICKS TONGUE]
Yeah, why not?

930
00:48:16,849 --> 00:48:17,981
Good for you.

931
00:48:19,286 --> 00:48:21,376
You're so angry.And you're not?

932
00:48:21,420 --> 00:48:22,333
Listen to me.

933
