about the things I did
and the things I didn't do...

935
00:48:30,994 --> 00:48:34,259
I know, and you were
going to be a great actress,

936
00:48:34,302 --> 00:48:36,914
and you were
beautiful and talented

937
00:48:36,956 --> 00:48:39,090
and you slept with all the men
under the moon.

938
00:48:39,132 --> 00:48:41,440
