when you died, Georgia.

941
00:48:52,277 --> 00:48:53,713
Good night.

942
00:49:01,764 --> 00:49:04,811
[GEORGE]:  I knew who that
pink flower was for.

943
00:49:04,853 --> 00:49:07,682
