944
00:49:07,726 --> 00:49:11,034
My short life was
like our family outings
to the circus.

945
00:49:11,860 --> 00:49:14,211
It wasn't so bad,

946
00:49:14,255 --> 00:49:18,650
a bit with a clown,
some cotton candy...

947
00:49:18,693 --> 00:49:21,175
And just as
things got interesting,

948
00:49:21,219 --> 00:49:22,523
